}}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== *16 x PoE+ Gigabit ports *4 x Gigabit Ethernet ports and 4 x shared SFP slots *Up to 30 Watts per port with a 185 Watts total power budget *40 Gbps switching capacity *Rack mountable
===Specifications=== *Processor: [[Realtek]] RTL8382M Multi-Layer Managed Switch Controller with Embedded MIPS-4KEc with MMU *Co-processor: Nuvoton MO516LDE to manage PoE *Flash/RAM: 32MB SPI Flash, 256MB DDR3 RAM
